  <brief_title>Laryngeal Injuries After Anesthesia Induction With Sevoflurane and After Anesthesia Induction With Rocuronium</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laryngeal Injuries After Anesthesia Induction With Sevoflurane and After Anesthesia Induction With Rocuronium. A Randomized, Prospective, Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
