  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Anesthesia induction with sevoflurane is not associated with an increased incidence or
      severity of laryngeal injuries compared with an anesthesia induction with a muscle relaxant.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
